### Mailing Lists ###

Sign yourself up to the general mailing list and get notification of events:

* [groups.google.com/group/srobo](http://groups.google.com/group/srobo) for general Student Robotics related discussions
* [groups.google.com/group/srobo-elec](http://groups.google.com/group/srobo-elec) for Electronics and hardware development discussion
* [groups.google.com/group/srobo-web](http://groups.google.com/group/srobo-web) for Web page, subpages, IDE, forum and server development and discussion

### IRC ###
Join our IRC channel and chat with us: #srobo at irc.zepler.net. [find out more](https://www.studentrobotics.org/trac/wiki/IRC).

